        "content": "<p>Good afternoon:</p>\n<p>We have noticed for some time that the logo sometimes fails to load on the first call. <br>\nAs example:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot from 2026-06-18 14-33-40.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1494x180\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/dJGwzn6dzzdAZfM-nPJBJK5t/Screenshot-from-2026-06-18-14-33-40.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/dJGwzn6dzzdAZfM-nPJBJK5t/Screenshot-from-2026-06-18-14-33-40.png/840x560.webp\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"image.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"571x198\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/lgEUFEnoq4JTYSH7OhwwA_F1/image.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/lgEUFEnoq4JTYSH7OhwwA_F1/image.png/840x560.webp\"></p>\n<p>Has anyone else experienced this problem?</p>",
        "id": 604513023,
        "sender_full_name": "Daniel Vila",
        "timestamp": 1781786399
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Hmm, yes, I'm seeing the same:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-18 at 9.18.53 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1523x526\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/53090/b1htsDRE_4cCmehuPo2XJq2d/Screenshot-2026-06-18-at-9.18.53AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/53090/b1htsDRE_4cCmehuPo2XJq2d/Screenshot-2026-06-18-at-9.18.53AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
